---
title: Cheat's Lamb & Eggplant Moussaka with Cucumber Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: The Mediterranean sea will feel like it’s washed up on your kitchen table with a Greek-inspired moussake. It’s got all those lovable
additions such as saucy lamb and roasted eggplant to make layers upon layers of flavoursome goodness.
